            "title": "歐洲股市上漲 受益於法國政局趨穩和雀巢股價飆升",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/4WMrmkoRYDxY.pSpA4Yarg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/4d74f35fb3efed831a3dc3f1dbe62368\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 歐洲股市上漲，此前法國總理挺過兩項不信任動議投票。食品巨頭雀巢公佈改革計畫後股價大漲，也為市場帶來支撐。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">斯托克600指數收盤上漲0.7%，法國CAC 40指數攀升1.4%。法國總理勒科爾尼在宣布暫停一項爭議性養老金法案的計畫後得以繼續留任。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場對法國政局的發展表示歡迎，「因為解散議會仍是他們最擔心的情形，」ING Belgium SA首席投資策略師Vincent Juvyns表示。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">個股方面，雀巢股價在公司執行長Philipp Navratil宣布將裁員1.6萬人後飆升逾9%。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-57b2a32f-d2d7-31e5-9efb-01151f932220-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/OhY43m.QMcI4cfkeidRxLw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/c08a9e6277f7fc401894fd107ef6b5d4\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由於對中美貿易戰的擔憂削弱了風險情緒，歐洲股市近期漲勢有所減弱。隨著第三季度財報季進入高峰期，公司盈利狀況成為市場焦點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題European Stocks Rise With French Politics in Focus; Nestle Jumps</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Julien Ponthus.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%B2-%E5%8F%97%E7%9B%8A%E6%96%BC%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%B1%80%E8%B6%A8%E7%A9%A9%E5%92%8C%E9%9B%80%E5%B7%A2%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E9%A3%86%E5%8D%87-165946080.html",
